Package: libclam1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: libclamcore1, libclamprocessing1, libclamvmfl1, libclamaudioio1, libclamvmqt1
Description: runtime package for the CLAM framework
 The CLAM framework is a C++ framework meant for helping
 to build applications that analyze, synthesize or transform
 digital signals - either music or audio.
